description: Support to the Establishment of Maternity & Children's Hospital in Fallujah

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description:
1. Access to and quality of secondary-level maternal, reproductive and paediatric health facilities in Fallujah improved.
2. Hospital staff capacity to provide quality secondary level maternal, reproductive and paediatric health care  strengthened. 
3. Awareness among the wider population on the establishment of the hospital and resulting “dividend of peace” raised
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: Falujah Hospital Establishment
